Excellent! Now I found the key module - `module_27` - which is the Enrichment Orchestrator. This is exactly what I was looking for. The code at lines 216-217 shows the critical bottleneck:

```rust
let (in_tx, in_rx) = mpsc::channel(CHANNEL_DEPTH);
let (out_tx, out_rx) = mpsc::channel(CHANNEL_DEPTH);
```

With `CHANNEL_DEPTH = 1_024`, this is the bounded mpsc channel that connects stages. Let me now look at the ingestion module and storage module to complete my understanding, and then identify the main orchestration that ties everything together.

